{% extends 'layout.html.twig' %}

    {% block title %}
        Home
    {% endblock %}

    {% block link %}
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/home.css">
        <script src="/script/Rules.js" defer ></script>
    {% endblock %}



{% block content %}


            <section class = "Rules">
                
                <div class="crossHome">
                    <div class="lineOne"></div>
                    <div class="lineTwo"></div>
                </div>

                    <h2 class="rulesTitle"> Rules </h2>
                    <p>Hi everyone!!
                        Welcome in the Stercket Battle, the place where you can catch all the sterckets around the world.
                        It's looks like a pokemon game but this is widely better! believe me!
                        Who is not fed up of these endless fights and this stressful music.
                        To remedy this there is a solution and this is....the.....
                        STERCKET BATTLE !!
                        So let's begin!</p><br>
                        

                    <p> If you want to start a new game then click on the New game button.
                        This lauch a new game and automatically create your first stercket randomly generated.
                        What a freaking world! You can see there are others wild sterckets who appears at the edge of the forest.</p><br>

                    <p> You can choose one among them by clicking on its image to select it.
                        After choosing lauch the combat between your stercket and the wild stercket you selected just before by clicking on the battle button.
                        A new event comes, it's the result of the combat between your stercket and the wild stercket.</p><br>

                    
                    <p> If your stercket win the combat the wild stercket is now part of your sterkets collection, if not your stercket is now a little weak and you must click on the button Rest to restore its health. Its the same concerning the wild stercket if you won the combat.</p><br>  
                    <p> From this moment you can choose the stercket of your choice in your collection to combat a wild stercket. </p><br>
                    <p> If you want resume your last game then click on the Resume button then you'll retrieve your sterckets collection. Funny isn't it?!
                        So it's time to play!</p>

            </section>

            <div class="PresentationButton">
                <section class= "blockPresentation">
                    <h2 class="welcome">Welcome In </h2>
                    <h2 class="StercketBattle"> STERCKETS </h2>
                    <h2 class="StercketBattle"> BATTLE </h2>
                </section>
            
{% endblock %}




{% block button %}
    <section class = "blockButton">
        <a class="button buttonContinue" href="../Game/play">Continue</a>
        <a class="button buttonPlay" href="../Home/initialise"> Play </a>
        <button class="button buttonRules" id="buttonRules" > Rules </button>
        
    </section>
</div>

{% endblock %}





